snippet.title: Chacara Teaser - Retro PS1-Style Horror Game set in the Amazon Rainforest
snippet.description: Chacara is a horror game with thriller and slasher features, retro aesthetics and PS1/PSX graphics, inspired by games from developers like Puppet Combo, the game takes place in the early 90's, in northern Brazil.
